# Source Images Directory

Place your original images here (JPEG, PNG, WebP).

The build script will generate optimized AVIF, WebP, and JPEG versions in multiple sizes from these source images.

## Supported formats:
- .jpg / .jpeg
- .png  
- .webp

## Naming convention:
Use descriptive names without spaces or special characters:
- ✅ hero-banner.jpg
- ✅ product-showcase.png
- ✅ team-photo.webp
- ❌ Hero Banner!.jpg
- ❌ my image (1).png

## Image guidelines:
- Upload high-quality source images (at least 1920px wide)
- The script will automatically generate smaller responsive sizes
- Avoid uploading already compressed/optimized images
- Original aspect ratios will be preserved